					<description><![CDATA[<p>Five local companies form consortium to build what Malaysia has never had. No funding secured, no anchor customer, and the clock is running. SEMICON SEA 2026: local players still don&#8217;t own an advanced packaging process. The number that stopped the room at MITEC on Wednesday afternoon was not the target. It was the starting point. [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://techwireasia.com/2026/05/malaysia-advanced-packaging-semiconductor-mapc-2035/">Malaysia wants 7% of the global advanced packaging market by 2035. Right now, it has zero.</a> appeared first on <a href="https://techwireasia.com">TechWire Asia</a>.</p>
